<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FAQ Section</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <style>
.container-c1 {
    width: 1296px;
    height: 523px;
    margin-top: 5968px;
    margin-left: 312px;
    font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;
    gap: 0;
}

.container-c2 {
    width: 416px;
    height: auto;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.faq-title {
    width: 416px;
    height: 120px;
    font-family: Poppins;
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 60px;
    text-align: left;
    color: #121519;
}

.faq-content {
    width: 416px;
    height: 72px;
    font-family: Poppins;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 24px;
    text-align: left;
    color: #ffffff;
    background: #576071;
    padding: 8px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

.container-c3 {
    width: 746px;
    height: auto;
    margin-left: 550px;
    gap: 16px;
}

.accordion {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
}

.accordion-item {
    width: 746px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 24px;
    background: #f0f0f0;
    transition: height 0.3s ease;
}

.accordion-item.active .accordion-answer {
    display: block;
}

.accordion-question {
    width: 650px;
    height: 28px;
    font-family: Poppins;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 27px;
    text-align: left;
    color: #051D40;
    cursor: pointer;
}

.accordion-answer {
    display: none;
    width: 650px;
    font-family: Poppins;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 24px;
    text-align: left;
    color: #051D40;
    margin-top: 16px;
}

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container-c1">
        <div class="container-c2">
            <h1 class="faq-title">Any questions? Check out the FAQ</h1>
            <p class="faq-content">Certainly! The FAQ section provides answers to common questions. It covers a variety of topics and aims to address user queries efficiently.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="container-c3">
            <div class="accordion">
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <div class="accordion-question">Q. Is Kiran Pratibha Scholarship awarded only to economically challenged students?</div>
                    <div class="accordion-answer">Yes, more than one student from the same family can also apply for the scholarship.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <div class="accordion-question">Q. Can more than one student from the same family apply for KPS?</div>
                    <div class="accordion-answer">Yes, more than one student from the same family can also apply for the scholarship.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <div class="accordion-question">Q. How long do you provide scholarship to the students?</div>
                    <div class="accordion-answer">Yes, more than one student from the same family can also apply for the scholarship.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <div class="accordion-question">Q. What are the major check points for scholarship?</div>
                    <div class="accordion-answer">Yes, more than one student from the same family can also apply for the scholarship.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <div class="accordion-question">Q. What is the expectation of Kiran Foundation from the students selected in KP?</div>
                    <div class="accordion-answer">Yes, more than one student from the same family can also apply for the scholarship.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.querySelectorAll('.accordion-question').forEach(item => {
            item.addEventListener('click', event => {
                const accordionItem = item.parentNode;
                accordionItem.classList.toggle('active');
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
